scene.message:
Mark: I wonder if there's{nl}
anyone else suffering{nl}
besides Sonomura.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I'm worried about how{nl}
Maki's mother is faring...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Let's hurry to the shrine!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You know, I figured{nl}
{ctl0f:1} would be more of a{nl}
weakling, but you're{nl}
surprisingly composed.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: I can't reach any of{nl}
the patients... What on earth{nl}
am I supposed to do?{waitkey}Couldn't you do something?{nl}
...{wait_fr:32}No, of course not. I'm{nl}
sorry, I'm all flustered...{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: I want to save as{nl}
many people as I can. You,{nl}
too — don't push yourself.{waitkey}{ret}
